VIETNAM GIRL AFTER MONEY NOT LOVE, SPREADS SEX DISEASE   
Dear A.S.S. Editor Advertisement 
My Friend know this age 22 Vietnam girl from Johor club The Zon and paramount. She claim that she was just looking for love but her motive was money. The most selfish act was she actually had sex transmitted diseases. 
When my Friend got know her, she was acting shy but quite outgoing. After a few chat at WeChat, they went out for a walk, "sort" of dating, but she at first act like so innocent to go bed with him, but after they had Sex, she wanted 100RM from my Friend. After a few time of bedding, my Friend start feeling itching of his private area and notice bubble spot around. So he went to see doctor and found out that he had this sickness. 
I'm out to inform all man outside to be extra careful with this following girl carrying STD. 
Car Toon
